        "description": "Aim to isolate x.",
        "workingLatex": "3x - 7 \\le 5",
        "explanation": "We isolate the term in $x$, keeping the inequality sign as we work.",
        "diagram": null
      },
      {
        "stepNumber": 2,
        "description": "Add 7 to both sides.",
